Domestic Gas Consumption

This info window shows average domestic gas consumption per meter for the area of City of London 001A in City of London in 2008 and 2009. The map is shaded by 2009 average values

Consumption per meter in 2008: 13,213 KwH

Consumption per meter in 2009: 12,312 KwH

London average 2009: 15,060 KwH

Mapping and analysis by: Alasdair Rae, 2011

Data Source: Department of Energy and Climate Change, 2011
